'''Miss Coruscant''' was the title of the winner of a [[Miss Coruscant talent and beauty pageant|talent and beauty pageant]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. [[Larisselle Chatrunis]] was Miss Coruscant shortly before the start of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

